modName: Tisdans Honeyside - A small Honeyside Mod
summary: This Mod just adds a satchel near the alchemy-table and a strongbox on the enchantment-table
descriptionHtml:
This small mod just adds a satchel and a strongbox to your Honeyside-House in Rifton. Nothing more.
I made this mod a while ago and now I want to share it with you.

This Mod is very simple. I don't need more containers or a room for a smelter and so on. So if you're like me and only want storage for your Alchemy and your Soul Gems, this Mod is for you.

[Installation]
1. Put it in your load order and activate it.

[Deinstallation]
1. Remove any Items from the Satchel and from the Strongbox
2. Delete this mod.

This mod has no dirty edits!

My mod may be incompatible with any mod that makes changes to the Honeyside House.
Please report any incompatible mod and I'll try to find a solution.

[Optional Files]
You'll find an optional file in the download section. This file just adds one chest and one strongbox.
You don't need the main file.



[Feature-Plans]
- Currently none so far, just ask me and I'll add them ;)
author: Tisdan
